::Zardus::

Zardus frowns and continues on, the three Alliance members' footsteps making echoes off of the bare metal walls. He glances around him, rounding another corner and aiming his gun at the vine that had grown through the large crack in the wall just in case it was a bot.

"My scanners have confirmed that there is something functional here, but they can't locate or identify it," he says, reaching into a compartment and taking out his sword. He approaches the vine, slashing through it and motioning for Wheeljack and Hurricane to do the same.
